ivardefs.name: contact
ivardefs.desc: An e-mail, phone, website or other contact point to use to resolve issues with message communications.

ivardefs.name: endpoint
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the routing target to send acknowledgements to.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: Human-readable name for the source system.

ivardefs.name: software
ivardefs.desc: May include configuration or other information useful in debugging.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: Can convey versions of multiple systems in situations where a message passes through multiple hands.

properties.desc: The source application from which this message originated.
